des:
Connect your Smart Stove App to Alexa in order to conveniently control it with just your voice!
Connect Alexa to your Smart Pellet Stove in a few simple steps: 
(1) Download the "Smart Stove" app in Google Play or iOS App Store;
(2) Launch the app and register a new account (or log in if you’re already registered);
(3) Turn on your pellet stove and connect it with the "Smart Stove" app;
(4) IMPORTANT: You can rename the pellet stove unit in the "Smart Stove" app;
(5) Download “Amazon Alexa” app from Amazon Market, Google Play or iOS App Store and connect Echo with “Alexa” app;
(6) Search the Alexa Skills directory for "NS Smart Stove" skill;
(7) Click to enable "NS Smart Stove" skill, and you’ll be navigated to Smart Stove login page;
(8) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(9) Setup is complete and you are now ready to use voice control.
Voice Commands include the following:
“Alexa, turn on [device name].”
“Alexa, turn off [device name].”
“Alexa, what is the temperature of [device name]?”
“Alexa, what is the target temperature of the [device name]?”
“Alexa, set [device name] to [75] degrees.”
